creator: MKT Apps
descriptionHtml:
Odia Barnabodha is a primary entry to odia literature. It is written by Madhusudan Rao. This App is made for people to correct their errors in odia language.

In this app we have tried you to give you the experience of reading barnabodha book in your smartphone.

Hope you guys enjoy this book. Never forget to give us rating on play store.
descriptionShort: A book app to learn odia language easy.
title: Odia Barnabodha - Easy To Learn Odia
